title: Plea deal offered to Capitol rioter accused of wielding stick at cops - Reuters
description: Prosecutors have proposed a plea bargain to a Virginia man accused of attacking police with a large stick during the Jan. 6 U.S. Capitol riot, lawyers for the government and defendant told a court hearing on Wednesday.
